── SUMMARY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
This block upgrades the visual polish of ALL pages across all
profiles to match the premium quality of the login page.

── GLOBAL CHANGES ──────────────────────────────────────────
1. Border radius: 4px → 12px across ALL inline styles (25+ files)
2. Border radius: 2px → 8px on secondary elements (5 files)
3. Added premium CSS utilities to globals.css:
   - .premium-card — glass card with 12px radius & hover effects
   - .stat-card — KPI display card with hover elevation
   - .stat-value / .stat-label — consistent metric typography
   - .page-header-title / .page-header-subtitle — page headers
   - .section-title / .section-divider — section separators
   - .th-premium — table header cells
   - .empty-state-premium — enhanced empty states
   - .premium-action-btn — CTA buttons
   - .gold-accent-bar — gold gradient section divider
4. Updated design-tokens.ts glass preset: blur 12px→16px, borderRadius: 12px
5. Updated prof-glass-card CSS: added border-radius: 12px
6. Upgraded bg-black/40 glass pattern: rounded-lg → rounded-xl

